<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="560" height="213" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/dfc2f9382ebf571dfa289816a852d61f-3-560x213.png" alt="" class="wp-image-196931" srcset="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/dfc2f9382ebf571dfa289816a852d61f-3-560x213.png 560w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/dfc2f9382ebf571dfa289816a852d61f-3-350x133.png 350w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/dfc2f9382ebf571dfa289816a852d61f-3-768x292.png 768w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/dfc2f9382ebf571dfa289816a852d61f-3-1536x584.png 1536w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/dfc2f9382ebf571dfa289816a852d61f-3.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px" /></figure></div>
<p>伶仃的夜裡，一个人的寂寞要如何排解？许多人会选择打开 A 片，想像与片中男女主角们来一场云雨巫山⋯⋯</p>
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3bb83d1bf5dda08fa11e1aa324ae1c92-560x373.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-194806" width="521" height="347" srcset="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3bb83d1bf5dda08fa11e1aa324ae1c92-560x373.jpg 560w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3bb83d1bf5dda08fa11e1aa324ae1c92-350x233.jpg 350w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3bb83d1bf5dda08fa11e1aa324ae1c92-768x512.jpg 768w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3bb83d1bf5dda08fa11e1aa324ae1c92-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3bb83d1bf5dda08fa11e1aa324ae1c92.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 521px) 100vw, 521px" /><figcaption>情色影音提供人们想像，纾解身心寂寥。图／<a href="https://pixabay.com/zh/photos/people-man-woman-couple-2589818/">pixabay</a>。</figcaption></figure></div>
<p>A 片的确解决了人们的生理需求，抚慰了心灵缺口，却也成为不少人的焦虑感、自卑感来源，尤其是 A 片男主角异常雄壮的——「阴茎」。</p>
<p>够不够粗？够不够长？够不够坚挺？当我们焦虑着自己是否「达标」时，就免不了好奇别人的尺寸，因此，人们流传着许多秘方，教我们用「身体的其他部位」间接判断性器官长度，像是脚掌长度、鼻子形状和身高等。</p><div class="pansc-content"></script>
